    "body": "Ah ok, I understand why I was always getting the map range.\nSeems that when all similar units on screen are already selected, the hotkey directly skips to the map range.\n\nI think there was only 1 rifleman on my screen (very early game, scouters). By selecting it, it's considered that all riflemen on screen are already selected. Probably that's why it was skipping the screen range. \n\nIt's clearer for me now, thanks ! \n"
